                        {
                            "type": "p",
                            "children": "For type sizes we use four GEL recommended breakpoint groups to suit a range of devices. Using the GEL breakpoints helps create uniformity across different screen sizes and capabilities. The sizes shown below correspond to size and line-height (size/line-height) and are in pixels. We do not kern or track Reith."
